WEBVTT

03:35.477 --> 03:44.084
Today we are celebrating the great event

03:44.283 --> 03:49.354
of the resurrection of Christ.

03:51.729 --> 03:58.150
On the same pattern is your resurrection;

03:58.539 --> 04:08.736
that you have risen to the new life of Divine love.

04:23.063 --> 04:35.791
You were all in the knowledge that
there’s something higher has to happen to you;

04:36.856 --> 04:47.158
that you are to be born again, but nobody knew how it works.

04:48.088 --> 04:58.217
The subtle side of your being was never told to you.

04:59.431 --> 05:03.862
The saints only talked as to how you should behave.

05:03.989 --> 05:14.373
They only said how you should try to keep a very pure life,

05:14.854 --> 05:24.421
sincere life, but they didn't tell you how it will work out.

05:24.965 --> 05:33.333
Of course people knew in India about it,

05:33.532 --> 05:39.555
very few of them, very, very few of them,

05:40.395 --> 05:49.112
but now it's a worldwide knowledge through you people.

05:52.434 --> 06:03.720
Now while your Kundalini rises,
She is your Mother, She is your individual Mother,

06:04.005 --> 06:09.178
and She gives you the second birth.

06:09.919 --> 06:23.889
That's how you get connected to the Divine paradise.

06:25.624 --> 06:31.020
All this, if it is told without realization has no meaning,

06:31.172 --> 06:37.851
but people are given great ideas about it

06:37.970 --> 06:50.423
and also were promised that one day your resurrection will come.

06:51.291 --> 06:54.881
It is the greatest happening for you,

06:57.612 --> 07:01.040
is the greatest event of your life,

07:01.614 --> 07:10.204
and one must consider it’s very fortunate
that you have been able to achieve it.

07:11.235 --> 07:18.545
All this because also because you desired for it.

07:18.609 --> 07:33.624
In many of your lives
you have been desiring for the heavenly paradise.

07:34.637 --> 07:45.605
People have been going round in the
hills and dales seeking; doing all kinds of things.

07:46.223 --> 07:50.233
That's already done by you.

07:50.423 --> 07:57.325
You don't have to give up anything, no need to give up anything.

07:57.753 --> 08:03.503
This wrong idea; I should say an untimely idea.

08:05.030 --> 08:13.974
This is the time when you have to get your
Sahaja resurrection, spontaneous resurrection.

08:15.266 --> 08:22.007
You don't have to do anything about it,

08:22.157 --> 08:28.763
it's just so simple as that; has worked out so well.

08:29.358 --> 08:38.232
I was really very much overjoyed to see that so many people,

08:38.368 --> 08:43.840
specially Muslims, about whom I have been so much worried

08:44.055 --> 08:47.456
that how can you save these people?

08:47.972 --> 08:55.241
They are so much lost in the mess of wrong thinking.

08:58.611 --> 09:06.890
One has to understand that this Koran was written

09:07.291 --> 09:12.437
forty years after the death of Mohammed Sahib.

09:13.350 --> 09:17.714
So maybe that there might be some words which are being,

09:17.792 --> 09:29.786
just being shifted maybe,
and the meaning might be little bit ambiguous.

09:30.945 --> 09:41.811
Also there was another book called Sunna came out about the same time

09:42.594 --> 09:49.557
and was managed by a person who was not such a great

09:49.717 --> 09:55.375
soul I should say, because he was not a realized soul.

09:55.974 --> 10:03.902
I can't understand how can you religiously understand a poet same

10:04.167 --> 10:11.090
and in the poetry whatever is written,
how can you interpret it correctly?

10:11.336 --> 10:17.699
This is the reason why I, I am a poet also;

10:17.850 --> 10:22.673
I could have written a poetry about it but I said no.

10:22.816 --> 10:30.883
Poetry can twist, can be twisted and also people can misuse it.

10:31.359 --> 10:34.078
That’s the problem with the poetry is.

10:34.429 --> 10:37.135
In India we had the same problem.

10:37.772 --> 10:42.047
For example, Kabira wrote such beautiful poetry

10:42.317 --> 10:45.904
and the way they interpreted was so nonsensical

10:45.974 --> 10:52.891
and so much different from the spirit of Kabira's songs.

10:53.137 --> 10:58.838
About everything they can twist the words

10:58.920 --> 11:07.861
according to their own need,
I found out if I wrote poetry about Divinity.

11:09.516 --> 11:12.826
This exactly what has happened.

11:12.945 --> 11:20.652
In all the religions I’ve seen,
when it comes to poetry people can twist it.

11:21.231 --> 11:34.920
Also, like in Bible, it was so much accepted

11:35.099 --> 11:45.830
that Paul is the one who is going to organize
the publication about Christ,

11:47.576 --> 11:52.177
