26:29.974 --> 26:33.294
Those who are pure people are Sufis.

26:33.556 --> 26:43.943
In the purity they see nothing
but Divine grace, Divine love, Divine peace.

26:44.085 --> 26:48.868
They talked of peace only; they could not talk of war.

26:49.116 --> 26:58.916
Anybody who talks of war cannot be a person who
has got any right to do that.

