All these six things, sixth one is the greed,

28:29.846 --> 28:39.007
all these six things that we had in our mind - out of
our ignorance, out of our upbringing,

28:39.248 --> 28:43.443
out of our reading, whatever it is,

28:43.562 --> 28:49.387
whatever we had developed, we were having - just drops out.

28:50.509 --> 28:57.008
When the Kundalini rises and you become one with the Divine,

28:57.112 --> 29:01.048
