31:04.496 --> 31:16.111
Secondly, if you read the story about
the birth of Shri Ganesh

31:16.275 --> 31:24.042
and then you proceed on, you’ll be surprised is written down
that it was called as Brahmand -

31:24.321 --> 31:32.367
means the egg of the Brahma that came into existence,

31:32.733 --> 31:40.648
and half of it became the Mahavishnu means the Christ,

31:40.751 --> 31:47.171
and half of it remained as Shri Ganesh.

31:47.512 --> 31:57.331
