36:14.608 --> 36:19.518
I mean there's a big celebration of baptism by these priests.

36:19.824 --> 36:24.581
Then where is the Sahasrara and where is the Kundalini

36:24.627 --> 36:27.702
and how do you have your second birth?

36:28.170 --> 36:33.055
There's no second birth, just some priest puts his hand on your head.

36:33.240 --> 36:38.032
Actually it makes a problem for realized souls,

36:38.215 --> 36:42.845
to put hand of the priest who are not realized souls,

36:43.218 --> 36:46.552
and that creates a problem for children.

36:46.577 --> 36:50.503
I have seen many children they start crying loudly

36:50.615 --> 36:54.713
when they are being blessed by these priests,

36:55.522 --> 36:59.480
because they are realized souls and the priests are not.

36:59.587 --> 37:02.007
It's very interesting.

37:02.094 --> 37:06.361
But they say, “After all you see it's the priests that are bad,

37:06.405 --> 37:11.122
but not Christ.” But how are they related to each other?

37:11.359 --> 37:15.834
Christ stood for morality.

37:17.603 --> 37:25.554
And about Him also in these modern times
they are saying all kinds of filthy things.

37:25.795 --> 37:35.439
They cannot understand a character
which is moral; to this extent we have gone.

37:37.237 --> 37:41.128
Morality is out of question.

37:41.740 --> 37:48.364
You do whatever you like; as long as
you go to church and confess, you’re all right.

37:49.126 --> 37:54.865
These are the absurdities of modern religions.

37:55.068 --> 38:03.343
Every religion has problems and the worst  I feel,
when you have

38:03.667 --> 38:07.550
the support of the world as your leader -

38:07.670 --> 38:15.296
how can you allow people to have such a immoral life?

38:17.794 --> 38:27.263
Immorality how can you tolerate when you follow the example of Christ?

38:27.722 --> 38:31.269
Out of question!

38:31.620 --> 38:36.501
He is the embodiment of morality.

38:36.645 --> 38:44.690
He is Shri Ganesh and how can you allow people

38:45.159 --> 38:49.667
to come to churches, to the temples,

38:50.091 --> 38:55.591
and allow them to have immoral life?

38:56.012 --> 39:00.681
What is the atonement for such people?

39:01.728 --> 39:12.836
The basis of Christ's life, the whole being
of Christ is morality; to establish purity.

39:15.386 --> 39:22.185
Now, it was Shri Ganesha who was created first

39:22.375 --> 39:30.474
by the Adishakti, because She wanted purity around.

39:32.307 --> 39:38.876
She wanted human beings to enjoy their purity

39:38.955 --> 39:48.536
and their personality which was emitting light to others.

39:49.067 --> 39:55.407
If there is impurity say for example on a glass

39:55.673 --> 40:02.714
and if you use that glass on top of the light,
how can the light pass out?

40:03.372 --> 40:11.337
The impure life cannot, cannot give light to others,

40:11.392 --> 40:15.292
and cannot show your inner light also.

40:15.356 --> 40:23.672
Both things are absolutely true about impurities.

40:24.286 --> 40:28.523
But people say that we have to accept

40:28.635 --> 40:33.666
because if you have to have more people for your religion

40:33.740 --> 40:40.142
you should accept many things, and one of them is impurity.

40:42.740 --> 40:45.078
And just think of it.

40:45.209 --> 40:49.976
Now at the Agnya where Christ resides,

40:50.246 --> 40:56.087
if your eyes are impure, full of lust and greed,

40:56.858 --> 41:04.949
then you are against Christ; you are an antichrist.

41:06.367 --> 41:13.966
If your eyes are clean and pure,

41:14.290 --> 41:23.592
then only you can enjoy love of God, otherwise you cannot.

41:24.635 --> 41:32.057
And also the love of another Sahaja Yogi or Yogini you can only enjoy

41:32.140 --> 41:36.933
in completeness if your eyes are clean.

41:37.020 --> 41:39.436
Just imagine.

41:40.046 --> 41:49.737
But if you have roving eyes and all sorts of things, I don't know

41:50.095 --> 41:54.724
how can you call yourself Christians? You cannot.

41:55.679 --> 41:59.960
Whatever certificate you may carry, but you are not,

42:00.129 --> 42:07.498
because those who are following Christ
have to have absolutely a moral life.

42:08.022 --> 42:16.028
That's a compulsion of the inner being on you -

42:16.228 --> 42:22.065
that you enjoy your morality

42:22.574 --> 42:29.807
and you enjoy above all your clean eyes.

42:31.150 --> 42:41.783
This is what I have come to know about the Western life
that the eyes are not clean.

42:41.918 --> 42:46.822
They’ll go to the church and their eyes will be moving here and there.

42:46.974 --> 42:49.244
How can that be?

42:49.276 --> 42:51.685
How can you do that?

42:51.710 --> 42:58.691
If you think Christ is the one who was resurrected
and you are to be resurrected,

42:58.767 --> 43:05.075
first of all see that you have pure love in your eyes.

43:05.458 --> 43:13.519
Now pure love is not relative, cannot be contaminated,

43:13.852 --> 43:19.058
cannot have lust and greed in them.

43:20.633 --> 43:26.234
These two things have to drop out from your mind completely.

43:26.814 --> 43:36.290
These are the days of people having greed, lots of greed they have.

43:38.765 --> 43:42.468
I just don't know what sort of things they have because

43:42.556 --> 43:46.814
I haven't studied so much the immorality of human being.

43:47.676 --> 43:52.222
Whatever I see are beautiful people like you.

43:52.601 --> 44:00.382
But when I try to understand the so-called Western culture

44:00.541 --> 44:06.141
I am surprised that even if they want to make a life for someone -

44:06.403 --> 44:11.792
like “The Life of Shakespeare” I saw,
who was according to Me

44:11.991 --> 44:20.157
was Avadhoota; means a person who has gone beyond all human

44:20.448 --> 44:28.415
destructive habits, Avadhoot is a very high quality yogi -

44:28.629 --> 44:35.160
and they show him as a stupid man running after a woman.

44:35.502 --> 44:47.322
They cannot conceive of human beings
who could be morally perfect, who will have moral sense.

44:47.393 --> 44:56.061
They cannot conceive, because those
who do this kind of thing are not realized soul.

44:56.290 --> 44:58.651
They are not Sahaja Yogis.

44:58.754 --> 45:04.451
So the conception about morality doesn't come into their head.

45:04.610 --> 45:07.628
They think as we are like that, the others are.

45:07.681 --> 45:12.312
Actually mostly they do it to justify themselves.

45:12.479 --> 45:23.999
So ugly and so horrifying is the depiction
of the character of such great people

45:24.126 --> 45:32.857
who talk such great things, shows that human beings
are really degraded in their value system.

45:32.990 --> 45:40.978
They cannot conceive of somebody who is an ideal personality.

45:41.337 --> 45:49.917
They think by saying so they are talking of something beyond reality.

45:49.972 --> 45:52.937
They don't know reality.

45:54.444 --> 45:58.365
Yesterday’s Sufi thing, I was very impressed

45:58.390 --> 46:01.709
when they said about the four stages that you have.

46:02.867 --> 46:07.576
And out of that the Haakikat - means the reality,

46:07.878 --> 46:12.433
you have to get into the reality.

46:13.284 --> 46:15.486
Reality is what?

46:15.898 --> 46:18.979
It’s not a perception.

46:19.162 --> 46:24.708
It's not seeing something, but it’s being something.

46:27.249 --> 46:34.300
If you start seeing, you might see something
white, red, yellow but you are not that.

46:34.513 --> 46:43.557
When you are, you are the reality,
then you emit reality,

46:43.874 --> 46:49.742
you see reality, you enjoy reality, you live in reality.

46:49.917 --> 46:55.028
This is real life and you don't indulge into

46:55.092 --> 47:02.373
something which is unreal, imaginary or below dignity.

47:02.398 --> 47:03.944
No you don't do it.

47:04.047 --> 47:09.152
You are the reality, is the Haakikat, as they say.

47:09.228 --> 47:15.685
You are the reality and you are emitting reality

47:15.741 --> 47:23.151
in your behavior, in your talks, in your lives, in everything.

47:25.730 --> 47:35.420
All this brings forth the greatest force of spirituality.

47:38.299 --> 47:46.724
Whatever is falsehood, whatever is wrong, whatever is destructive,

47:47.256 --> 47:53.500
will run away from a man who stands in reality; is automatic.

47:55.818 --> 48:00.719
It is absolutely part and parcel

48:00.925 --> 48:06.231
of the same personality who is supposed to be a realized soul.

48:06.776 --> 48:12.395
So the resurrection has taken place no doubt - all right.

48:12.648 --> 48:15.218
Your hands are speaking - all right.

48:15.377 --> 48:27.122
I don't want to give you any command or
any kind of a fixed road that you have to follow.

48:27.443 --> 48:31.693
Now you are free, because you have the light.

48:31.795 --> 48:34.778
When you have the light why should I tell you which way to go?

48:34.803 --> 48:43.793
You know yourself that you have the light,
so you follow yourself in a way

48:43.888 --> 48:49.241
that is an enlightened path, with your own light.

48:49.368 --> 48:53.398
Don’t somebody has to tell you
hat don't do this, don't do, nothing of the kind.

48:53.581 --> 48:58.847
You want just do it, if something wrong
you will not do; if you are doing it

48:58.881 --> 49:04.916
then know that you have to still rise above all this thing.

49:05.519 --> 49:11.510
You are the Nabhis that are described in the Koran.

49:11.750 --> 49:17.081
You are the ones who are going to resurrect the whole world.

49:17.240 --> 49:24.573
You are the ones who are going to help the downtrodden people

49:24.709 --> 49:30.219
into the filth of immorality. Your life should show.

49:30.346 --> 49:39.430
Look at these few of these people who were Sufis,

49:39.621 --> 49:46.849
who were very clean people, how have they been able to channelize

49:47.206 --> 49:50.407
the other people into a better life?

49:51.202 --> 49:53.617
That is what you are.

49:53.780 --> 49:59.275
You have to channelize their lives; that's your job.

49:59.397 --> 50:07.157
Don't think about what is happening,
how the people are stupid, immoral, forget it.

50:07.412 --> 50:10.222
What you have to know what you are.

50:10.310 --> 50:17.831
You have to be aware of yourself
and of your responsibility as being the purest of pure.

50:18.206 --> 50:22.857
As my name is indicates, you are My children,

50:22.956 --> 50:28.773
and that indicates the children of Nirmal, means purity.

50:29.008 --> 50:34.768
Purity is the basis of your existence.

50:35.624 --> 50:41.757
You should try to see where, what you were, in which part.

50:42.029 --> 50:47.658
There’s no mistake in appreciating the art,

50:47.817 --> 50:54.237
appreciating all that is beautiful, appreciating all

50:55.007 --> 50:59.444
that is created out of beautiful minds,

50:59.547 --> 51:04.345
but there should be no lust and greed in that appreciation.

51:04.640 --> 51:10.155
Pure appreciation, purity is the message,

51:10.209 --> 51:15.737
and once you have the purity within yourself you will love yourself.

51:16.012 --> 51:19.361
As I love you, you will love you also.

51:19.409 --> 51:26.263
And then you will understand this word love
which comes out of the purity.

51:26.550 --> 51:35.698
The blossoming of your purity,
the fragrance of your purity, you enjoy all the time

51:35.839 --> 51:41.841
and the love that you have flows,

51:41.952 --> 51:48.602
flows towards all those who are to be loved,
who have to be looked after.

51:48.919 --> 51:55.208
Don’t worry about the people who are destructive.

51:55.377 --> 52:00.403
That's the only word I can use,
because there are so many things one can say about.

52:00.602 --> 52:05.792
Let them be destructive because they are destroying themselves.

52:05.893 --> 52:08.474
Why should we worry about them?

52:08.545 --> 52:10.987
They think they are destroying others but they are not,

52:11.122 --> 52:15.802
they are destroying themselves.
So forget about it, just forget.

52:15.955 --> 52:25.657
You think yourself to be responsible for the construction
of the whole world,

52:25.724 --> 52:28.444
it's not only a few people.

52:28.762 --> 52:33.485
You are very intelligent, knowledgeable and understanding.

52:33.580 --> 52:38.196
You are not like the Disciples of Christ who were not educated,

52:38.223 --> 52:46.118
who didn't understand so much and
who did get realization but were not of your level.

52:46.772 --> 52:54.943
Whatever they could do reached to a point
where this kind of a mess of a Christianity has come,

52:55.347 --> 52:58.279
but you can't create that kind.

52:58.363 --> 53:08.386
You will create a new vibrant religion which is global.

53:08.607 --> 53:14.899
I was very happy to see that now
we have people from all over the world.

53:15.145 --> 53:17.771
It’s a global movement all over.

53:18.311 --> 53:25.350
It has nothing to do with the limited ideas of so called religions.

53:25.636 --> 53:28.747
They have ruined every religion.

53:28.786 --> 53:37.011
Islam is ruined, Christianity ruined,
and Hinduism ruined, and Buddhism the worst.

53:37.524 --> 53:40.554
In Buddhism you give up everything -

53:40.729 --> 53:48.007
all your belongings, all your property, give to the guru, imagine!

53:48.436 --> 53:55.924
And the guru is so greedy horrible fellow.

53:56.763 --> 54:03.319
How can he give resurrection?
Himself is a greedy fellow,

54:03.534 --> 54:09.397
misleading others just taking away everything.

54:10.424 --> 54:13.985
Then same thing about Christianity

54:14.088 --> 54:17.091
that you all become Nuns,
you become Fathers, you become

54:17.116 --> 54:20.869
Brothers and I don’t know, all nonsense.

54:21.126 --> 54:24.646
But there's no change within.

54:25.947 --> 54:32.056
Somebody came to Me and I said, “Why did you become a priest?”

54:32.145 --> 54:34.855
He said, “Because I was jobless.

54:36.212 --> 54:37.957
I had no job.”

54:37.957 --> 54:38.957
Baba?

54:38.957 --> 54:41.399
“So I took up the job of a priest.”

54:41.478 --> 54:42.938
Can you imagine?

54:43.576 --> 54:50.503
He could not fit into any job, so the minimum of minimum
he took is this job.

54:50.830 --> 54:53.060
Then what did you do?

54:53.234 --> 54:59.704
“They told me what I have to preach and first I had to practice

55:00.122 --> 55:04.614
and remember it by heart, and then I don't know,

55:04.738 --> 55:11.650
I started talking this, talking that.”
I said he must be a big possessed man.

55:11.817 --> 55:17.286
He had no mind of his own; he didn't know what he was talking.

55:17.421 --> 55:24.087
He would take out one sentence from Bible
and go on talking, boring everybody.

55:24.268 --> 55:31.499
And I was surprised that within fifteen minutes
people wanted to get out of the church.

55:31.865 --> 55:39.372
As soon as the sermon was over they would run out
and breathe, “Thank God.”

55:40.126 --> 55:44.109
Is that what religion gives you?

55:44.324 --> 55:46.977
Is that what should happen to you?

55:47.096 --> 55:49.980
No, it's not that.

55:50.124 --> 55:56.287
What happens to you that
you enjoy yourself, you enjoy the collectivity,

55:56.312 --> 55:58.586
you enjoy the goodness, the morality.

55:58.586 --> 56:04.669
The whole thing is like the nectar of life.

56:05.848 --> 56:10.407
So that changes the whole picture.

56:10.954 --> 56:17.707
The ritualism is so much; in the Hindu religion
there is too much of ritualism.

56:17.964 --> 56:25.461
You sit on the right or you sit on the left;
you do this at this time I mean, lots of it.

56:25.625 --> 56:30.459
That when your sister dies how many days you should starve yourself;

56:30.484 --> 56:33.876
if your husband dies then how many days?

56:34.810 --> 56:40.198
Dies is died, finished; the body’s finished now.

56:40.569 --> 56:44.920
So you fast for so many days - is very wrong,

56:44.945 --> 56:48.631
because you’re fasting the bhoot might come in to you.

56:51.637 --> 56:57.380
But still, what I would say all these ritualisms and all that,

56:57.520 --> 57:05.972
are created by human beings
who were claiming to be something great.

57:06.160 --> 57:13.284
They are not; by no means they are the people in charge of morality,

57:13.331 --> 57:18.274
in charge of higher life.

57:18.845 --> 57:24.388
They lead such a mundane useless life.

57:26.473 --> 57:29.667
I went to a temple of Shri Ganesha,

57:29.751 --> 57:35.791
which is supposed to be Swayambhu,
one of the eight temples; it is one of them.

57:39.061 --> 57:40.768
And I was surprised.

57:40.793 --> 57:50.016
The man who was worshipping was supposed to be the priest,
he was suffering from paralysis,

57:50.590 --> 57:58.110
and his brother died of paralysis, now his son was also paralyzed.

57:58.396 --> 58:01.524
He said, “What is this Ganesha doing to us Mother?”

58:01.549 --> 58:05.059
I said, “What are you doing to Ganesha?

58:05.321 --> 58:09.331
How much money you earn out of it?”

58:09.434 --> 58:12.043
He said, “Quite a lot.”

58:12.305 --> 58:14.560
“And then what do you do with this money?

58:14.585 --> 58:17.429
Do you do anything for the society?

58:17.454 --> 58:19.979
Do you try to improve their lives?

58:20.004 --> 58:26.541
Have you any attention on the society
or you are just ooking after yourself?”

58:26.696 --> 58:33.168
As a result, he’s got paralysis,
his brother got paralysis, son got paralysis.

58:33.567 --> 58:37.213
And he was blaming Ganesha for that.

58:37.713 --> 58:42.455
He said, “Is it a real Ganesha?”
“Yes it is, but you are not.

58:42.765 --> 58:45.841
You don't deserve.”
I told him off on his face.

58:45.984 --> 58:49.415
He said, “All right you may say whatever you like but You cure me.”

58:49.534 --> 58:54.802
I said, “First promise that whatever money you get out of this temple

58:54.827 --> 58:59.646
you will spend it for the betterment of people.”

59:00.605 --> 59:03.636
But how can they?

59:05.080 --> 59:07.460
They are not realized souls.

59:07.563 --> 59:12.833
Such a lot of priests I see walking about with all this funny dresses.

59:12.873 --> 59:13.873
What?

59:14.064 --> 59:21.193
These are like dead bodies,
walking around with all kinds bad vibrations.

59:22.019 --> 59:24.214
I can't understand.

59:24.482 --> 59:30.442
And the other people are very simple,
they say, "Oh my goodness, see now he’s a priest."

59:30.641 --> 59:32.514
So they must respect.

59:32.539 --> 59:36.251
But, they don't see it; they do not ascertain

59:36.276 --> 59:43.876
what is the spiritual value of that person
who calls himself as the priest.

59:45.290 --> 59:47.420
That is your job.

59:47.523 --> 59:49.142
You don't have to fight with them.

59:49.167 --> 59:51.016
You don't have to denounce them.

59:51.016 --> 59:54.137
You don't have to describe them.

59:54.137 --> 59:57.977
No need, but understand that you are different.

59:57.977 --> 01:00:01.852
You have the right. You are the authority

01:00:02.066 --> 01:00:05.221
and so with that authority and confidence

01:00:05.246 --> 01:00:08.316
you have to go about and save people.

01:00:08.316 --> 01:00:11.765
You are realized souls.

01:00:11.918 --> 01:00:14.619
You got your resurrection.

01:00:14.651 --> 01:00:20.681
You are yogis; I agree, but what is your job?

01:00:20.967 --> 01:00:23.358
Why, why this has happened?

01:00:23.445 --> 01:00:30.238
Why this light has come in to you is to take the blind

01:00:30.897 --> 01:00:36.178
in your hands and take them towards the light.

01:00:36.416 --> 01:00:40.293
This is what is your resurrection for.

01:00:40.468 --> 01:00:49.803
It's not only for your seeking but also is the grace of the Divine,

01:00:49.917 --> 01:00:54.985
for you to make the whole world Divine, as far as possible.

01:00:55.070 --> 01:00:58.009
How many people have you given realization?

01:00:58.089 --> 01:01:00.123
How many people you have talked to them?

01:01:00.148 --> 01:01:03.550
I tell you I was surprised; once I was traveling by plane

01:01:03.670 --> 01:01:07.194
and there was some lady traveling with Me

01:01:07.219 --> 01:01:12.142
and she started talking to Me about her cult, about her nonsense.

01:01:12.167 --> 01:01:15.799
So look at it, shamelessly she was talking.

01:01:16.076 --> 01:01:21.624
Listening to her I said, Sahaja Yogis won't,
they won't talk about Sahaja Yoga.

01:01:21.851 --> 01:01:27.615
Every person who is a Sahaja Yogi has to talk about Sahaja Yoga,

01:01:27.805 --> 01:01:32.133
may not be with the wrong type but with the right type of people.

01:01:32.645 --> 01:01:37.027
That's a thing you have to do. That's why you are enlightened.

01:01:37.394 --> 01:01:42.180
You are not enlightened to be put somewhere in the forest

01:01:42.688 --> 01:01:45.623
or to be lost to the whole world.

01:01:45.648 --> 01:01:51.497
You are enlightened; you are resurrected to enlighten other people.

01:01:51.607 --> 01:01:54.936
That's what you are there for

01:01:55.500 --> 01:01:58.090
and you can do it. Many have done it.

01:01:58.131 --> 01:02:00.452
So many of you have done it,

01:02:00.507 --> 01:02:07.101
and I would say that all of you, whether
you are a man or a woman, you have to do it.

01:02:08.784 --> 01:02:19.247
And that's the request of your Mother - t
hat make use of your realization.

01:02:19.885 --> 01:02:26.350
And the attention should be only on realization.

01:02:26.735 --> 01:02:31.888
How many people you are going to give realization to?

01:02:32.125 --> 01:02:36.012
How many people you are going to save?

01:02:36.893 --> 01:02:39.957
Is a very simple job for you.

01:02:40.014 --> 01:02:41.995
You have to just raise the Kundalini.

01:02:42.093 --> 01:02:43.143
You can.

01:02:43.286 --> 01:02:47.802
You should see how just with your hand
you can raise the Kundalini of others

01:02:47.827 --> 01:02:50.507
and give them their resurrection.

01:02:50.909 --> 01:02:53.155
You don't have to do anything.

01:02:53.180 --> 01:02:56.424
The life is not that difficult for you.

01:02:56.463 --> 01:03:00.622
Your job is the easiest thing; it’s just to raise your hand.

01:03:00.647 --> 01:03:03.098
In hand, in your hand you have the power,

01:03:03.173 --> 01:03:11.976
just to raise your hand and give them realization,
instead of feeling diffident.

01:03:13.373 --> 01:03:17.891
That's why I would say you are all resurrected,

01:03:17.979 --> 01:03:20.832
you are all realized souls,

01:03:21.000 --> 01:03:24.602
and you have to create the Divine paradise on this earth.
